This collection contains 128 miscellaneous record books from Troup County, Georgia, for the years 1827â€“1969. They include

deeds and homestead records

registers of medical practitioners

court records

city directories

war records

bond books

and other types of records.

The records vary widely in the types of details they contain, but they are typically good sources for names and dates. This is an image-only collection, meaning you will need to browse the books, but most have an index at the beginning that will aid in your search.
